data.description: Positioned on a corner lot with welcoming street presence, this meticulously maintained two-story home that is nestled in the heart of Cramerton, is a definite must-see! Offering elegance, functionality, and convenience, this beautiful residence features a covered front porch, back patio and fenced backyard. The main level features modern luxury vinyl flooring, guiding you seamlessly through the open floorplan for relaxation, dining, and entertaining. The kitchen showcases stainless appliances, granite counters, an island bar, and a coveted walk-in pantry. Upstairs, discover a separate laundry room and four spacious bedrooms, one currently utilized as a versatile game/music/lounge room. The owner's suite boasts a generously sized bedroom with cathedral ceilings, an ensuite bath with enclosed shower and dual vanities, and an oversized walk-in closet that will truly amaze. Enjoy effortless access to schools, shopping, and restaurants, ensuring every convenience is within easy reach.
